data.text:
Our 2023 summer musical is Broadway's Tony Winning show! Sit back and watch this madcap musical comedy about love in the roaring 20s. Money, wealth, fame, love, the mafia and even roller-skating mix it up in this joyful send-up of a fictional musical called "The Drowsy Chaperone!". A great show for the entire family.

Show dates are July 20th - 30th. Thursday - Saturday at 7:30 pm. Saturday and Sunday Matinee at 3:00pm. Tickets for "The Drowsy Chaperone" go on sale on June 22nd!
